<div id="banner">
	<h1>Make Mozilla Money Fast!</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>David Hyatt: <a href="http://mozillazine.org/weblogs/hyatt/2002_08_04_mozillian_archive.html#85327266">How to Monetize(tm) your browser</a>.</p><blockquote><img align="right" src="http://www.mozillazine.org/weblogs/hyatt/menu1.PNG" />The first monetizing technique I&#8217;ll show you is called &#8220;Stealth Infection.&#8221; Under the principle of stealth infection, you must insert ties to your Web properties in seemingly innocuous locations. The idea is to rely on the user&#8217;s poor hand-eye coordination. They&#8217;ll be shooting for Open File.. and they&#8217;ll end up buying furniture instead! It&#8217;s brilliant! It cannot fail!</blockquote><p>They&#8217;re clearly getting desperate. Be sure to <a href="http://mozillazine.org/weblogs/hyatt/2002_08_04_mozillian_archive.html#85327266">read the rest</a>, the funniest part is still to come.</p>

